01:04:27.610 --> 01:04:34.360
Archaic relied on space-time
inventions such as rituals

01:04:34.360 --> 01:04:37.390
not only to mark space
in particular ways,

01:04:37.390 --> 01:04:43.450
as you saw in the example of
Madurai in Southern India.

01:04:43.450 --> 01:04:49.060
But in crude form, this
is the same phenomenon,

01:04:49.060 --> 01:04:52.690
the bringing together
of people in public

01:04:52.690 --> 01:04:56.990
to celebrate a
particular thing--

01:04:56.990 --> 01:05:00.250
in the case, a race,
which has meaning which

01:05:00.250 --> 01:05:05.140
is meaningless, in the
second, a celebration

01:05:05.140 --> 01:05:12.060
to return people after being
captured by a foreign nation.